#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.182"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.182:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.182:0.2"
msgid "19. Brāhmaṇavagga "
msgstr "19. Brahmins "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.182:0.3"
msgid "182. Pāṭibhogasutta "
msgstr "182. Guarantee "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.172, sc1
msgctxt "an4.182:1.1"
msgid "“Catunnaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ natthi koci pāṭibhogo—"
msgstr "“There are four things that no-one can guarantee—"

msgctxt "an4.182:1.2"
msgid "samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā devo vā māro vā brahmā vā koci vā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "not an ascetic, a brahmin, a god, a Māra, a Brahmā, or anyone in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.182:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.182:2.2"
msgid "‘Jarādhammaṃ mā jīrī’ti natthi koci pāṭibhogo—"
msgstr "No-one can guarantee that someone liable to grow old will not grow old. "

msgctxt "an4.182:2.3"
msgid "samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā devo vā māro vā brahmā vā koci vā lokasmiṃ; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.182:2.4"
msgid "‘byādhidhammaṃ mā byādhiyī’ti natthi koci pāṭibhogo—"
msgstr "No-one can guarantee that someone liable to sickness will not get sick. "

msgctxt "an4.182:2.5"
msgid "samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā devo vā māro vā brahmā vā koci vā lokasmiṃ; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.182:2.6"
msgid "‘maraṇadhammaṃ mā mīyī’ti natthi koci pāṭibhogo—"
msgstr "No-one can guarantee that someone liable to death will not die. "

msgctxt "an4.182:2.7"
msgid "samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā devo vā māro vā brahmā vā koci vā lokasmiṃ; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.182:2.8"
msgid "‘yāni kho pana tāni pubbe attanā katāni pāpakāni kammāni saṅkilesikāni ponobhavikāni sadarāni dukkhavipākāni āyatiṃ jātijarāmaraṇikāni, tesaṃ vipāko mā nibbattī’ti natthi koci pāṭibhogo—"
msgstr "No-one can guarantee that the bad deeds done in past lives—corrupted, leading to future lives, hurtful, resulting in suffering and future rebirth, old age, and death—will not produce their result. "

msgctxt "an4.182:2.9"
msgid "samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā devo vā māro vā brahmā vā koci vā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.182:3.1"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ dhammānaṃ natthi koci pāṭibhogo—"
msgstr "These are the four things that no-one can guarantee—"

msgctxt "an4.182:3.2"
msgid "samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā devo vā māro vā brahmā vā koci vā lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "not an ascetic, a brahmin, a god, a Māra, a Brahmā, or anyone in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.182:3.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
